                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-47-off234 t17880402-47-cd235"></join>, seventeen yards of printed cotton, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880402-47-victim491" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Potts
                  <interp inst="t17880402-47-victim491" type="surname" value="Potts"></interp>
